α : Type u,
_inst_1 : inhabited α,
b : buffer α,
i : ℕ,
h : i < b.size
⊢ b.read ⟨i, h⟩ = b.read' i

α : Type u,
_inst_1 : inhabited α,
i b_fst : ℕ,
b_snd : array b_fst α,
h : i < size ⟨b_fst, b_snd⟩
⊢ read ⟨b_fst, b_snd⟩ ⟨i, h⟩ = read' ⟨b_fst, b_snd⟩ i

α : Type u,
_inst_1 : inhabited α,

b_snd : array b_fst α,
h : i < size ⟨b_fst, b_snd⟩
⊢ b_snd.read ⟨i, h⟩ = b_snd.read' i

α : Type u,
b : buffer α,
i : ℕ,
h : i < b.size,
v : α
⊢ b.write ⟨i, h⟩ v = b.write' i v

α : Type u,
i : ℕ,
v : α,
b_fst : ℕ,
b_snd : array b_fst α,
h : i < size ⟨b_fst, b_snd⟩
⊢ write ⟨b_fst, b_snd⟩ ⟨i, h⟩ v = write' ⟨b_fst, b_snd⟩ i v

i : ℕ,
v : α,

⊢ ⟨b_fst, b_snd.write ⟨i, h⟩ v⟩ = ⟨b_fst, b_snd.write' i v⟩
